Powers.DescShort: Auto Res Placate, Disorient, Terrorize, Smashing, Lethal, Fire, Cold, Toxic
Powers.DescLong: Demonlings are resistant to Placate and Disorient effects.  They are also resistant to Lethal, Smashing, Fire, Cold and Toxic damage.  They can also hurl Ice Bolts at their foes.
Two quick Swipes with your claws. Does minor lethal damage, but has a quick recharge rate. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Very Fast
Ice Bolt quickly pelts an enemy with small icy daggers; their chill Slows a foe's attacks and movement for a time. Fast, but little damage. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Fast
